## Supervision

I supervise and mentor students at different stages of their academic careers, including PhD candidates, Master’s students, and early-career researchers.

- [**Elvira González-Salmón**](https://sites.google.com/go.ugr.es/egonzalezsalmon/). Niños furbito y niñas lo que sea: The gender gap in science and the consequences for the scientific knowledge that is created. University of Granada. Ongoing
- [**Victoria Di Césare**](https://sites.google.com/view/vdicesare). El costo de realizar
investigación local: implicaciones para las trayectorias científicas y la
producción de conocimiento. University of Granada. Ongoing
- [**Néstor Mir Planells**](https://nestormirplanells.wordpress.com/). Universitat Politècnica de Valéncia. Ongoing
- [**Alwaleed Alkhaja**](https://creativecommons.org/person/alwaleed-alkhaja/) University of Tampere On-going